import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; import { IAddress } from '../address.model'; @Component({ selector: 'jhi-address-detail', templateUrl: './address-detail.component.html', }) export class AddressDetailComponent implements OnInit { address: IAddress | null = null; constructor(protected activatedRoute: ActivatedRoute) {} ngOnInit(): void { this.activatedRoute.data.subscribe(({ address }) => { this.address = address; }); } previousState(): void { window.history.back(); } }
